comment_regular_data.body:
Yes. When completepopup is present, the logic here will be as follows.

```C
int max_extra = MAX(right_extra, left_extra);
int final_width = max_extra;
bool used_user_width = false;
if (completepopup_width_opt > 0 && max_extra > completepopup_width_opt) {
    final_width = completepopup_width_opt;
    used_user_width = true;
}
if (final_width < 10 && !used_user_width) {
    wp->w_config.hide = true;
    return false;
}

wp->w_config.width = final_width;
```
